<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Removal Job Request Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #4CAF50;
        }
        .job-details {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .job-details p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .job-details strong {
            color: #333;
        }
        .cta {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h2>Your Removal Job Request Has Been Received</h2>
    <p>Hello, {{clientName}}</p>
    <p>Thank you for your removal job request. Below are the details you provided:</p>

    <div class="job-details">
        <h3>Your Information</h3>
        <p><strong>Name:</strong> {{clientName}}</p>
        <p><strong>Phone Number:</strong> {{clientPhone}}</p>
        <p><strong>Email Address:</strong> <a href="mailto:{{clientEmail}}">{{clientEmail}}</a></p>

        <h3>Job Details</h3>
        <p><strong>Start Address:</strong> {{startAddress}}</p>
        <p><strong>Destination Address:</strong> {{destinationAddress}}</p>
        <p><strong>Move Date and Time:</strong> {{moveDate}} at {{moveTime}}</p>
        <p><strong>Distance:</strong> {{distance}}</p>


        {{#if furnitureDetails}}
            {{#if furnitureDetails.length}}
                <h3>Furniture Details</h3>
                <ul>
                    {{#each furnitureDetails}}
                        <li>{{item}} - Quantity: {{quantity}}</li>
                    {{/each}}
                </ul>
            {{/if}}
        {{/if}}

        <!-- Conditional Appliance Details Section -->
        {{#if applianceDetails}}
            {{#if applianceDetails.length}}
                <h3>Appliance Details</h3>
                <ul>
                    {{#each applianceDetails}}
                        <li>{{item}} - Quantity: {{quantity}}</li>
                    {{/each}}
                </ul>
            {{/if}}
        {{/if}}


        <h3>Boxes and Special Items</h3>
        <p><strong>Small Boxes:</strong> {{smallBoxes}}</p>
        <p><strong>Medium Boxes:</strong> {{mediumBoxes}}</p>
        <p><strong>Large Boxes:</strong> {{largeBoxes}}</p>
        <p><strong>Extra Large Boxes:</strong> {{extraLargeBoxes}}</p>
        <p><strong>Special Items:</strong> {{specialItems}}</p>
    </div>

    <p>Once a driver is assigned to your job, we will contact you with further details.</p>

    <p>If you have any questions in the meantime, feel free to reach out to us at <a href="mailto:eremovalsscot.gmail.com">eremovalsscot.gmail.com</a>.</p>

    <p>Thank you for choosing Eremovals!</p>
    <p>The Eremovals Team</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
